title: Tico ASMR: Un Punto de Luz Palido (ASMR en Español)
description:
On this special edition of Sleep and Relax ASMR, our friend Jerry from Tico ASMR  discusses Carl Sagan and his book "A Pale Blue Dot," or "Un Punto de Luz Palido," in Spanish. This episode is entirely in Spanish. Enjoy!
